snippet.title: Wiki Edit History Analyzer
snippet.description: The Wiki Edit History Analyzer processes the MediaWiki revision history and produces summaries of edit actions performed. Basic edit actions include insert, delete, replace, and move; high-level edit actions include spelling correction, wikify, etc.
